snippet.title: Kana Quest Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Kana Quest Makes Friends With Japanese Alphabet On Steam March 12

Kana Quest is puzzle game where you help the Japanese alphabet make friends by matching the sounds between letters. And in doing so you learn how to read Hiragana or Katakana. 

Wishlist now at: 
bit.ly/2RA5tjb

Follow At:
https://twitter.com/KanaQuest
https://www.facebook.com/KanaQuest/
